This folder contains useful tools for developers.

clear-whitespace.rb
  Clear all trailing white space in a file.
  Usage: ./clear-whiltespace.rb <path-to-file>

nova.vimrc
  This file provides some useful settings for vim.

style-check.rb
  Check coding style of all source code files in Nova.
  You can fix all the bad styles with an '-f' option.
  Usage: ./style-check.rb

